OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNigel Pearson: Veteran     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fspeedway commentator dies  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Faged 52                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tributes have been paid to the sports  
OL,6, journalist and commentator Nigel       
OL,7, Pearson.                               
OL,9,FHis family said the 52-year-old died on
OL,10,FFriday after being taken ill suddenly  
OL,11,Fearlier in the week.                   
OL,13,FMr Pearson, a former BBC Radio         
OL,14,FHumberside speedway reporter, went on  
OL,15,Fto work on national TV and radio.      
OL,17,FSky Sports, who Mr Pearson worked for  
OL,18,Fas a darts commentator for 15 years,   
OL,19,Fsaid he "was a consummate broadcaster  
OL,20,Fwith a distinctive voice".             
